Package csw.alarm.models

Class AlarmSeverity

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.alarm.models.FullAlarmSeverity
      • csw.alarm.models.AlarmSeverity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    enumeratum.EnumEntry, enumeratum.EnumEntry.Lowercase
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlarmSeverity.Critical$, AlarmSeverity.Indeterminate$, AlarmSeverity.Major$, AlarmSeverity.Okay$, AlarmSeverity.Warning$
    public abstract class AlarmSeverity
extends FullAlarmSeverity
    Represents the alarm severity set by the component developer e.g Okay, Warning, Major, Indeterminate, Critical. Disconnected is not a part of AlarmSeverity as it is never set by the component developer.

    param: level is fundamental in comparing severities
